title: Dallas 10x24 Some Good, Some Bad.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the dream is over, its even better than ever!

J.R. and Bobby receive surprising help towards getting Jamie's 10% of Ewing Oil; Cliff is questioned in Jamie's death and Pam learns of his shady deal with Jeremy Wendell; a visit to Ray's house leaves Bobby stunned.

First Aired: 3/20/1987

Instead of airing at it usual time, this episode originally aired an hour later at 10:00 p.m. (in the time slot that was normally occupied by Falcon Crest).

Dack Rambo returns briefly (and appears in the opening credits one last time) before leaving the show for good.
